OL,3,CMore criminal suspects in Horizon
OL,4,Cscandal as police request funding
OL,6,FReport by ITV News Investigation
OL,7,FProducer Isabel Alderson-Blench
OL,9,FThe police investigation into the Post
OL,10,FOffice Horizon scandal has expanded
OL,11,Fits list of suspects and warned that
OL,12,Fit could face delays if further
OL,13,Ffunding is not secured.
OL,15,FIn a briefing with sub-postmasters on
OL,16,FSunday, the officers in charge of
OL,17,FOperation Olympos said the total
OL,18,Fpersons of interest in the
OL,19,Finvestigation had reached 53, and the
OL,20,Fnumber of suspects was now eight.
