OL,6,FFive of the suspects have been
OL,7,Finterviewed under caution. The police
OL,8,Fhave not disclosed the names of any
OL,9,Fsuspects.
OL,11,FThe police officers leading the
OL,12,Finvestigation, Commander Stephen
OL,13,FClayman and Senior Investigating
OL,14,FOfficer Mick Norman, told victims that
OL,15,Fthe police operation had requested
OL,16,Ffurther funding from the Home Office,
OL,17,Fand without this, they could face
OL,18,Fdelays.
