OL,6,FThe Post Office has now confirmed it
OL,7,F"will not seek to enforce any non-
OL,8,Fdisclosure agreements (NDAs)" signed
OL,9,Fby sub-postmasters as part of the
OL,10,Fscandal, and the police encouraged any
OL,11,Fvictims who had signed an NDA and had
OL,12,Fnot yet come forward to do so.
OL,14,FThe police also told sub-postmasters
OL,15,Fthat they were seeking advice from the
OL,16,FCrown Prosecution Service on corporate
OL,17,Fand gross negligence manslaughter
OL,18,Fcharges.
