OL,6,FPreviously, police said they were "not
OL,7,Fruling out" corporate manslaughter
OL,8,Fcharges. However, they confirmed that
OL,9,Fperjury and perverting the course of
OL,10,Fjustice remain the key charges they
OL,11,Fare pursuing.
OL,13,FITV News also understands that from
OL,14,F2027, the police will be expanding the
OL,15,Finvestigation to look at the role Post
OL,16,FOffice and Fujitsu executives played
OL,17,Fin the scandal.
