OL,6,FMore than 100 officers are working on
OL,7,Fthe investigation, made up of regional
OL,8,Fteams across the UK. The volume of
OL,9,Fdocuments being reviewed by the police
OL,10,Fhas now reached 7.5 million.
OL,12,FAny potential criminal trials are not
OL,13,Fexpected to take place until 2028 or
OL,14,F2029.
OL,16,FFreedom of Information requests by ITV
OL,17,FNews reveal that so far, the police
OL,18,Finvestigation has run up costs of more
OL,19,Fthan #7 million, with an additional
OL,20,F#1.3 million provided via special
OL,21,Fgrants from the Home Office.
