OL,6,FThe projected police spend for 2025/26
OL,7,Fis around #10 million, and it is
OL,8,Funderstood that the funding being
OL,9,Frequested from the Home Office is in
OL,10,Faddition to this.
OL,12,FLee Castleton is a former sub-
OL,13,Fpostmaster and one of those who
OL,14,Fattended the police briefing call.
OL,16,FMr Castleton was sued by the Post
OL,17,FOffice for over #300,000 and made
OL,18,Fbankrupt after the Horizon system at
OL,19,Fhis Post Office in North Yorkshire
OL,20,Fshowed shortfalls of #25,000, which he
OL,21,Frefused to pay back.
