OL,6,FThe Post Office Horizon scandal is the
OL,7,Fmost widespread miscarriage of justice
OL,8,Fin British history. Between 1999 and
OL,9,F2015, more than 900 sub-postmasters
OL,10,Fwere prosecuted after faulty Horizon
OL,11,Faccounting software made it look as
OL,12,Fthough money was missing from their
OL,13,Faccounts.
OL,15,FA total of 236 sub-postmasters were
OL,16,Fsent to prison, and the total number
OL,17,Fof victims is estimated to be more
OL,18,Fthan 10,000.
